text: Andole–Jogipet is a town in Sangareddy district of Telangana, India. Jogipet municipal corporation was constituted in 2014. Jogipet municipal corporation is includes Jogipet town and Andole village,. The jurisdiction of the civic body is spread over an area of . MLA is Chanti Kranti Kiran (from 13 December 2018). == References == Category:Towns in Medak district
